message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been highly valued by our previous customers. Given its exceptional quality and functionality, we believe it's worth more than $100. However, to make this opportunity more appealing, I am offering it to you at a special introductory price of $95. This is an exclusive offer tailored for you, considering the value you place on high-quality products. Don't miss out on this chance to own something truly remarkable!
